author: Sheena McGinley
title: TV News | Watch: Hillary Clinton gets royally ribbed over her stance on same sex marriage on SNL
text:
It does get pretty buttock crinkling in parts - it's that close to the bone - but that's what SNL's Kate McKinnon does best... Here she plays "Madame President" Hillary Clinton blowing off some steam after a hard twenty three years, while presidential hopeful Hilary plays Val - just a bartending citizen that does a STERLING Donald Trump impression.
In case you're wondering why Miley Cyrus was also there - she managed to host the whole darn thing.
